### Approval Writeback Failures API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

###

### 1. 查询未解决的回写失败列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/writeback-failures?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 2. 手动重试指定失败记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/writeback-failures/1/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Length: 0
